node.text:
Exciting news!🎉

We teamed up with @hiresbigh to create a Salted Malted Chocolate Chip Cookie Milkshake!  The shake has vanilla ice cream, lots of our freshly baked cookies, and Hire’s famous salted caramel sauce! Yep, it’s AMAZING!😋

The shake is available this week (Monday-Saturday) at all Hires locations! If you live in Utah, you have to try it! Tag me and let me know what you think! We are going tonight and maybe every night! It’s that good!💯 #twopeasandtheirpod

node.text: Today is Maxwell’s 7th birthday and we have been celebrating all day! It’s been so much fun, but we are all anxiously awaiting cake time! He picked the chocolate celebration cake in our cookbook and I’m so glad because it’s my favorite too! I can’t wait to eat a big piece with my birthday boy! What is your favorite birthday dessert? 🎉🎂
